Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.88,0:33:39.26,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}ゆりかごで明日へ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.40,0:33:45.29,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}晴れの日も雨の日にも
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.61,0:33:49.98,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}あなたを守るために
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.46,0:34:00.89,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}かけがえのない宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.47,0:34:11.71,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}名前のない花は　静かに眠るよ
