Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.61,0:33:16.74,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}一隻小鳥 婉轉鳴叫著
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.39,0:33:27.80,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}在未知的天空中 四處尋找我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.21,0:33:33.62,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}在溫柔編織出的搖籃裡
